test_negate_of_divisors:
assert [-8, -8] == [-8]
  Left contains one more item: -8
  Full diff:
  - [-8]
  + [-8, -8]
test_list_of_zeros:
assert [0, 0] == [0]
  Left contains one more item: 0
  Full diff:
  - [0]
  + [0, 0]
test_coefficient_of_divisor:
assert [64] == []
  Left contains one more item: 64
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [64]
